5:
Cocoa, milk, sugar... That's
everything! Without your help, we
might not have had enough
ingredients to keep up with this
sudden influx of orders!
9:
It's no problem. I'm just glad we
made it in time for the festival.
13:
Yep. With how popular this
chocolate-giving confession fad
has gotten, I figured it'd be good to
replenish our stock before the
festival started!
17:
As a representative of the Guild
though, I'm thrilled about how
excited everyone is! Oh, and I'm
looking forward to being a judge
again this year!
22:
It seems to have spread to nearby
villages too! This is all thanks to you,
Alkâ€”
25:
E-excuse me! Ellya? Do you have a
moment?
28:
Oh, it's you! You just started
adventuring recently, didn't you?
What's up?
34:
I like you, Ellya!
Will you go out with me?
37: You... want to go out... with me?
47:
Sh-she said yes! Oh my gosh!
Thank you, Ellya!
58:
Already?!
It's only been a single day!
62:
Ellya... Just what did you do to the
poor boy?
67:
Huh? Why are you assuming it was
my fault?! We just went on a date,
that's all!
71:
But before we even reached the
Midways, he started apologizing...
and then ran off crying.
76:
You went to the Kaleidoscope?! On a
date?!
80:
Was... that bad? What are normal
couples supposed to do? I don't
know the rules!
82:
Plus, I figured there's no better way
to get to know someone than to see
how they act when their life is on the
line! Right?
91:
B-but... If we're thinking of a full
commitment, I have to make extra
sure that...
95:
Oof... I really messed up this time,
didn't I?
100:
Listen man, I get how you must be
feeling... but you really can't go
around sulking like that. It's been
days!
102:
Yeah! There are plenty of other fish
in the sea, man! Give up on Ellya
already!
105:
Well. It certainly wasn't a
trouble-free affair, but it looks like
the festival was an overall success.
114:
Well, if it isn't Ellya. You down to get a
few drinks?
118:
Oh, hi, everyone. I'm sorry, there's
something I need to take care of
first...
121: Hey, do you have a minute?
125:
I've been thinking... Ever since... well,
you know.
129:
I'm really pretty clueless when it
comes to love... But you know what?
I was honestly, genuinely happy
when you said you liked me.
136:
I made you some chocolate. I don't
think I can go out with you again,
but... I wanted to say thank you for
sharing your feelings with me.
139:
I'd like you to have it. If you want it,
that is.
144:
Of course I'll take it! Thank you!
And... I promise I'm going to do my
best to become the type of guy who
can be your equal!
147:
Hehe. I'm looking forward to seeing
that!
159:
For the rest of you!
Please have these chocolates!
169: Hehe, that's right! I had another idea.
173:
What if I started a new trend and
made it okay to give chocolates to
ANYONEâ€”not just people you're
romantically interested in!
176:
I got the idea reading about similar
gift-giving customs in Yamato!
179:
This way, everyone can get
chocolate, and nobody will feel left
out!
183:
So... You're just obligated to give
everyone chocolates?
188:
Yeah! That's a good
wordâ€”obligated! Nice one, Alk!
191:
Of course, I have chocolate for all of
you as well! Here you go.
201:
Is it me or does Alk's chocolate look
different from ours?
205:
That's right! He helped me out a lot
the other day, so his chocolate is
extra special!
209:
Hmm, we should also have a system
like that! The more helpful a person's
been to you, the nicer the chocolate
you get them!
214:
Haha... I don't know about this whole
"system" thing. Seems like a pretty
big chore...
223:
Ellya! Are you really THAT dense?!
How could you do that to the poor
guy?
227:
Wh-what? Why is everyone turning
on me all of a sudden?
232:
Way to build a man up just to tear
him down in front of everyone. That
was savage.
236:
Not you too, Nimbus! What is even
going on?
240:
Aghhh, why is this "love" thing so
damn complicated?! I don't get it!
